<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Contractor Supplemental Application - <%= data.segment || "Plumber" %></title>
  <style><%= styles %></style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Header Section -->
<div class="header-info">
  <div class="header-row">
    <div class="header-col">
      <strong>Contractors Supplemental Application - <%= data.segment || "Plumber" %></strong>
    </div>
    <div class="header-col" style="text-align: right;">
      <strong>Date:</strong> <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size: 10px; font-style: italic; margin-top: 5px;">
    TO BE USED WITH COMMERCIAL APPLICATIONS (ACORD 125 & 126)<br/>
    All questions must be answered in full. Application must be signed and dated by the applicant.
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========== APPLICANT INFORMATION ========== -->
<h2>Applicant Information</h2>
<div class="form-section">
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">Applicant's Name</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.applicant_name || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">Mailing Address</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.mailing_address || data.premise_address || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row cols-2">
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">Phone Number</div>
      <div class="form-value"><%= data.business_phone || data.applicant_phone || "" %></div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">Web Address</div>
      <div class="form-value"><%= data.web_address || "" %></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row cols-2">
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">Proposed Policy Period</div>
      <div class="form-value"><%= data.policy_period_from || "" %> to <%= data.policy_period_to || "" %></div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">Business Structure</div>
      <div class="form-value"><%= data.business_structure || "" %></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========== PREMISES INFORMATION ========== -->
<h2>Premises Information</h2>
<div class="form-section">
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">Location #1</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.location_1 || data.premise_address || "" %></div>
  </div>
  <% if (data.location_2) { %>
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">Location #2</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.location_2 %></div>
  </div>
  <% } %>
  <% if (data.location_3) { %>
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">Location #3</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.location_3 %></div>
  </div>
  <% } %>
</div>

<!-- ========== UNDERWRITING INFORMATION ========== -->
<h2>Underwriting Information</h2>
<div class="form-section">
  
  <div class="form-row cols-2">
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">1. How long has the applicant been in business?</div>
      <div class="form-value"><%= data.years_in_business || "" %> years</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">Years of experience in this field:</div>
      <div class="form-value"><%= data.years_experience || "" %></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">2. Is the applicant licensed?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.is_licensed || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row cols-2">
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">3. Your contractor's license number:</div>
      <div class="form-value"><%= data.license_number || "" %></div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">Type of license:</div>
      <div class="form-value"><%= data.license_type || "" %></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">4. Indicate the percent of each type of work performed:</div>
  </div>
  
  <table class="data-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>TYPE</th>
        <th>COMMERCIAL</th>
        <th>RESIDENTIAL</th>
        <th>INDUSTRIAL</th>
        <th>% OF TOTAL OPERATIONS</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>New Construction</strong></td>
        <td><%= data.commercial_new_construction || "" %>%</td>
        <td><%= data.residential_new_construction || "" %>%</td>
        <td><%= data.industrial_new_construction || "" %>%</td>
        <td><%= (parseInt(data.commercial_new_construction||0) + parseInt(data.residential_new_construction||0) + parseInt(data.industrial_new_construction||0)) %>%</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Renovation</strong></td>
        <td><%= data.commercial_renovation || "" %>%</td>
        <td><%= data.residential_renovation || "" %>%</td>
        <td><%= data.industrial_renovation || "" %>%</td>
        <td><%= (parseInt(data.commercial_renovation||0) + parseInt(data.residential_renovation||0) + parseInt(data.industrial_renovation||0)) %>%</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Real Estate Developer</strong></td>
        <td><%= data.commercial_developer || "" %>%</td>
        <td><%= data.residential_developer || "" %>%</td>
        <td><%= data.industrial_developer || "" %>%</td>
        <td><%= (parseInt(data.commercial_developer||0) + parseInt(data.residential_developer||0) + parseInt(data.industrial_developer||0)) %>%</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  
  <div class="form-row cols-2" style="margin-top: 10px;">
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">5. Indicate the percentage of work you perform as a General Contractor or as a Subcontractor:</div>
      <div class="form-value">(a) General Contractor: <%= data.pct_gc || "" %>% &nbsp;&nbsp; (b) Subcontractor: <%= data.pct_sub || "" %>%</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="form-label">Indicate the percentage of work on a typical project performed by:</div>
      <div class="form-value">(a) Your Employees: <%= data.pct_work_employees || "" %>% &nbsp;&nbsp; (b) Subcontractors: <%= data.pct_work_subs || "" %>%</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <% if (!data.segment || data.segment === "Plumber") { %>
  <!-- PLUMBER-SPECIFIC QUESTIONS -->
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">Perform any gas line work or hook-ups?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.gas_line_work || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">Any boiler work? (install, inspection, service, cleaning or repair)</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.boiler_work || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">High-pressure steam pipe installation, service or repair?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.high_pressure_steam_work || "" %></div>
  </div>
  <% } %>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">6. If residential construction, how many new detached single family homes per year?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.single_family_homes_per_year || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">11. Do you ever hire subcontractors?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.hire_subs || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">12. Are certificates of insurance required from subcontractors prior to the start of every project?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.subs_require_coi || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">14. Do you require your subcontractors to carry workers compensation?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.subs_wc || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">24. Do you have a written safety program?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.written_safety_program || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">29. Do you perform any out of state work?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.out_of_state_work || "" %></div>
    <% if (data.out_of_state_work === "Yes" || data.states_work_in) { %>
      <div style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 5px;">If yes, in what states? <%= data.states_work_in || data.out_of_state_details || "" %></div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">41. Do you carry workers compensation insurance?</div>
    <div class="form-value"><%= data.carry_workers_comp || "" %></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PAGE BREAK -->
<div class="page-break"></div>

<!-- ========== TYPE OF WORK PERFORMED ========== -->
<h2>Type of Work Performed</h2>
<div class="form-section">
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">Please indicate whether the following trades are: E – performed by your employees or S – performed by subcontractors</div>
  </div>
  
  <table class="data-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>DESCRIPTION</th>
        <th>E/S</th>
        <th>ANNUAL PAYROLL/COST</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><%= data.segment || "Plumbing" %></td>
        <td><%= data.trade_plumbing_by || "" %></td>
        <td><%= data.trade_plumbing_cost || "" %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Electrical</td>
        <td><%= data.trade_electrical_by || "" %></td>
        <td><%= data.trade_electrical_cost || "" %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Roofing</td>
        <td><%= data.trade_roofing_by || "" %></td>
        <td><%= data.trade_roofing_cost || "" %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>HVAC</td>
        <td><%= data.trade_hvac_by || "" %></td>
        <td><%= data.trade_hvac_cost || "" %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Excavation</td>
        <td><%= data.trade_excavation_by || "" %></td>
        <td><%= data.trade_excavation_cost || "" %></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<!-- ========== EXPERIENCE ========== -->
<h2>Experience</h2>
<div class="form-section">
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">1. What is your projected gross revenue / sales for the upcoming policy term?</div>
    <div class="form-value">$<%= data.projected_gross_revenue || "" %></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">2. Please provide your gross revenue / sales for the last three years:</div>
  </div>
  
  <table class="data-table">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Year 1 Gross Sales:</strong></td>
        <td>$<%= data.gross_sales_year_1 || "" %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Year 2 Gross Sales:</strong></td>
        <td>$<%= data.gross_sales_year_2 || "" %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Year 3 Gross Sales:</strong></td>
        <td>$<%= data.gross_sales_year_3 || "" %></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-label">5. Additional information or comments:</div>
    <div class="form-value comments-box"><%= data.additional_comments || "" %></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========== IMPORTANT NOTICES ========== -->
<div class="form-section" style="margin-top: 30px;">
  <h3 style="text-align: center;">PLEASE READ BELOW AND COMPLETE SIGNATURE BLOCK</h3>
  
  <div style="font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 15px 0;">
    <p><strong>WARRANTY STATEMENT:</strong> The purpose of the supplemental questionnaire is to assist in the underwriting process. Information contained herein is specifically relied upon in determination of insurability. The under signed, therefore warrants to the best of his knowledge, information and belief. The supplemental questionnaire, and the application to which it is appended, shall be the basis of any insurance policy that may be issued and will be part of such policy.</p>
    
    <p><strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE:</strong> As part of our underwriting procedure, a routine inquiry may be made to obtain applicable information concerning character, general reputation, personal characteristics, and mode of living. Upon written request, additional information as to the nature and scope of the report, if one is made, will be provided.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.3; margin: 15px 0; font-style: italic;">
    <p><strong>FRAUD STATEMENTS</strong></p>
    <p><strong>NOTICE:</strong> In some states, any person who knowingly presents a false or fraudulent claim for payment of a loss or benefit or knowingly presents false information in an application for insurance is guilty of a crime and may be subject to fines and confinement in prison.</p>
    
    <p><strong>Colorado:</strong> It is unlawful to knowingly provide false, incomplete, or misleading facts or information to an insurance company for the purpose of defrauding or attempting to defraud the company. Penalties may include imprisonment, fines, denial of insurance, and civil damages.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========== SIGNATURE BLOCK ========== -->
<div class="form-section" style="margin-top: 20px; border-top: 2px solid #000; padding-top: 20px;">
  <div style="font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <strong>APPLICATION MUST BE SIGNED BY APPLICANT</strong><br/><br/>
    I have reviewed this application for accuracy before signing it. As a condition precedent to coverage, I hereby state that the information contained herein is true, accurate and complete and that no material facts have been omitted, misrepresented or misstated. I know of no other claims or lawsuits against the applicant and I know of no other events, incidents or occurrences which might reasonably lead to a claim or lawsuit against the applicant. I understand that this is an application for insurance only and that completion and submission of this application does not bind coverage with any insurer.
  </div>
  
  <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 40px;">
    <div style="width: 45%;">
      <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #000; margin-bottom: 5px; height: 40px;"></div>
      <div style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Producer's Signature</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Date</strong></div>
    </div>
    <div style="width: 45%;">
      <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #000; margin-bottom: 5px; height: 40px;"></div>
      <div style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Applicant's Signature</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Date</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PAGE FOOTER -->
<div class="page-footer">
  Contractor Supplemental Application - <%= data.segment || "Plumber" %><br/>
  © Commercial Insurance Direct LLC
</div>

</body>
</html>
